---
layout: base.njk
title: 我的部落格
---

{% set newestPost = collections.posts | head %}

<main>
    {% if newestPost %}
        <h2>{{ newestPost.data.title }}</h2>
        <p class="post-date">發布日期: {{ newestPost.date | date: "%Y年%m月%d日" }}</p>
        {{ newestPost.content | safe }}
    {% else %}
        <h2>歡迎來到我的部落格！</h2>
        <p>目前還沒有文章。請稍後再回來看看！</p>
    {% endif %}
</main>
<aside id="sidebar">
    <h2>所有文章</h2>
    <ul id="post-list">
        {% for post in collections.posts %}
            <li><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></li>
        {% endfor %}
    </ul>
</aside>